data.description: Introducing a stunning new addition to the coveted community of Belleme Chateau in Otay Ranch! This immaculate two story 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom condo offers contemporary elegance and breathtaking views, all nestled on a private desirable corner lot. All New flooring throughout upstairs  Outside, soak in the stunning views from the comfort of your own private patio, where you can enjoy morning coffee or evening cocktails while taking in the beauty of the surrounding landscape.  Located in the sought-after community of Belleme Chateau, residents enjoy access to a variety of amenities, including parks ( Santa Venetia Community Park), Community Pool, walking trails, and A+Graded Veterans Elementary School and Mater Dei HS at the end of the sreet.. Plus, with convenient access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options, everything you need is right at your fingertips. Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Otay Ranch. With its prime location, modern features, and breathtaking views, this condo won't last long. Experience Belleme Chateau!
